name: Biggest Icon Library (svg format + in component state)
description:
This is the biggest high quality free icon library you can get on the Figma community. It contains all the popular icons we use daily in our designs like Heather icons, Hericons, Boxicons, Unicons, Google Material design icons , Font Awesome, Line Awesome and much more.

Just duplicate and publish the library and start using.

Enjoy your visual design.
